---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy | ZeroUpload";
const description =
  "ZeroUpload's privacy policy. Your files are converted entirely in your browser and are never uploaded, stored, or seen by us.";
const updated = "June 2026";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 pt-16 pb-20">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-stone">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <div class="article-body mt-8 space-y-4 text-stone leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink">The short version</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>We never receive your files.</strong> All conversions happen
        locally in your browser. Your files are not uploaded to, stored on, or
        processed by any ZeroUpload server — because there is no such server
        involved in the conversion.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink">Your files</h2>
      <p>
        When you convert a file, it is read into your browser's memory, converted
        on your device, and offered back to you as a download. It never travels
        across the internet. When you close or refresh the page, that data is
        gone from memory. We have no copy and never did.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink">Information we do collect</h2>
      <p>
        To run the website we may use privacy-respecting analytics to understand
        aggregate, anonymous usage (such as which pages are visited). This never
        includes the contents of your files. If we display advertising, ad
        partners may use cookies as described in their own policies; you can
        control cookies through your browser settings.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink">Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        The core converter works without requiring cookies. Any cookies used are
        limited to basic site functionality and, where applicable, advertising
        partners.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink">Children's privacy</h2>
      <p>
        ZeroUpload is a general-purpose utility and is not directed at children
        under 13.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink">Changes</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy from time to time. Material changes will be
        reflected by the "last updated" date above.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-ink">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about privacy? Email <strong>privacy@zeroupload.app</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .article-body :global(strong) {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
